Dia. 01 Black 2, Vital Point
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's tiger's mouth move is an often used technique.
\par However it is easy to find its weakness.\cf1\b  Black's vital point at 2 \cf0\b0 becomes obvious.
\par
\par White dies up to 4.
\par
\par
\par
