Dia. 02 Death Again
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par After White 1, Black 2 is the vital point again and White is captured easily.
\par
\par The vital point is at the same place in this and the previous variation as well.
\par
\par Hint: "\cf1\b The opponent's vital point is my vital point\cf0\b0 ".
\par
\par }
